Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:36.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:41.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟早会知道 Vajra真正的恐怖之处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:54.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开拍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:01.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是最新型VF-25
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:04.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:08.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍摄完成后会用CG加工成VF-0
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:10.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡 看见兰歌没
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.93,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌应该在海角那边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:14.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:16.68,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还是决定穿女装？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:18.95,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:20.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:24.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得有幸观摩传说中的男旦表演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:29.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转为接受了水下拍摄时的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:30.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替男主角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:33.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是47号镜头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.08,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:37.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真大胆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:39.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:40.68,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吻戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:41.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和玛奥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:47.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长 莫非不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:48.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:52.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那打算接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么大不了的 接吻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:03.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当真？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:07.68,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佑乘坐的车…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:22.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 来人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:28.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
