Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:51.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布瑞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:01.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:03.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然被Hydra…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:08.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:10.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:15.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:16.62,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:22.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直来救我 阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:32.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦掉眼泪 大家都在看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:36.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:39.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌 大新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:41.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超究极大新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我演玛奥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:52.23,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且想把兰歌的曲子作为主题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊 这样一来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:58.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:01.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你演玛奥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:03.08,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味着我和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:07.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要接吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:09.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:19.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过禁止采取引人怀疑的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:23.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想找回过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:26.38,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别再擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:29.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心搬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:47.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没马上答应？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:50.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意和阿鲁多接吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:00.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎还没能下定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:03.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难为她了 情况特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多你自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:13.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕自己做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:17.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论接吻还是演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:22.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不了解玛奥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:28.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上莎拉姐姐的心上人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:32.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后自己主动献出了吻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:36.68,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没真正恋爱过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:38.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:43.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:49.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:53.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过对她来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:07.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:17.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当真了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:24.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 看你紧张的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:28.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己口口声声说接吻没什么大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:37.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
