Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:15.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我能理解
